Understanding Why Bad Things Happen to Good People This article, in response to the Batman shootings, has people asking "How can God let this happen? How can God let such horrible things be done to His children? "
http://www.ldsmag.com/article/1/11162
These people just don't get it. God doesn't LET it happen. God MAKES it happen. God PLANS it to happen. And he's getting pissed that more people, unlike me, aren't giving thanks when he executes his plan. He has neither the time nor the inclination to explain himself to those who rise and sleep under the blanket of goodness that he provides, and then question the manner in which he provides it. He would rather you just said thank you, and went on your way. Let's get it together people - thank God!
